Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.99,0:00:07.96,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本片轻描淡写地讲述了南家三姐妹平凡的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.36,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要过度期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,thank you  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  美人姐姐的长袖和服装哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是烦人的姐姐才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  长袖和服很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  千秋也很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆敢对美人姐姐出言不逊于是就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  别逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来抓我试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我说  大正月的不要乱闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到是过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系哟  我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是千秋的错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  让夏奈转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.25,0:01:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经当不了新娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像古装剧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大正月就在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿和服所以稍等会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  尽情享受正月吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:37.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,310)}一年之计好像在于元旦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
